All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
AnalyticsCounter
Outputs a file with symptoms ordered alphabetically and their occurrences
CountSymptomDataFromFile
A counter that can count and order symptoms alphabetically from a file
Uses two for-loops to count the symptoms from a List variable


ISymptomCounter
Anything that will count symptoms

ISymptomReader
Anything that will read symptom data from a source
The important part is, the return value from the operation, which is a list of strings, that may contain many duplications

The implementation does not need to order the list

ISymptomWriter
Anything that will write symptoms and occurrences into a specified file
The symptoms must be ordered alphabetically and the file may not contain duplicates

ReadSymptomDataFromFile
Simple brute force implementation of reading a file line by line
WriteSymptomDataFromFile
Writes symptoms from a TreeMap to a result.out file
